cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CC, cs.IR 

This paper deals with natural language understanding and specifically focuses on the Story Cloze Test (SCT) task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also incorporates logic information to improve the understanding of the story, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper uses machine learning techniques to model the logic information, which is related to the category of Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with the task of natural language inference, which is related to Computational Complexity (cs.CC) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
